abstract: Leslie V. Norwalk, acting administrator of the Centers for Medicare and Medicaid Services, comes from a family of very strong women.
snippet: Leslie V. Norwalk, acting administrator of the Centers for Medicare and Medicaid Services, comes from a family of very strong women.
lead_paragraph: I COME from a family of very strong women. My mother’s mother, Nana, was a strong individual and had lots of opinions and made them known. And my mother likewise. She brought in a lot of money for the family as a real estate broker, and she had an enormous personality.
